  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“西太后”芝麻大的小事被粉红、岁静、黄左炒作批斗了一个多星期了还没消停。这帮人趁机攻击日本和台湾的移民政策，想借助舆论让日本放开移民。<br/>\r\n日本作为保守主义国家，还没放开移民，中国粉红已经闹翻天了。要是大面积放开中国的移民，要不了几年就成了粪坑。台湾、韩国这些国家也一样。<br/>\r\n美国和欧洲被移民搞得一团乱，黄左还在吹嘘“多元化”。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGQyMjE4MDljN2ZmZjhhMTYzZDQ5LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNjQx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d221809c7fff8a163d49.png?width=1080&amp;height=1641\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d221809c7fff8a163d49.png?width=1080&amp;height=1641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8d221809c7fff8a163d49.png?width=1080&amp;height=1641\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGNiYzY4OWM2NjhlOWExOWVlZjk2LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMDYz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4cbc689c668e9a19eef96.png?width=1080&amp;height=2063\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4cbc689c668e9a19eef96.png?width=1080&amp;height=2063\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4cbc689c668e9a19eef96.png?width=1080&amp;height=2063\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
